# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Binary files (never touch line endings / no diffs)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*.png    binary
*.jpg    binary
*.jpeg   binary
*.gif    binary
*.ico    binary
*.svg    binary
*.webp   binary
*.pdf    binary
